&lt;li&gt;Lead business development and sales efforts, including prospecting, outbound communication, and pipeline management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain customer records, track engagement, and contribute to detailed customer reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
