&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and productionize advanced techniques from graphics and computer vision research (e.g., Gaussian Splatting, radiance fields, compression, streaming).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver efficient, optimized code across the rendering pipeline and wring out performance from desktop, mobile and VR hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with researchers, engineers, and cloud/content teams to design end-to-end streaming and rendering solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with industry and academic advances, moving ideas quickly from concept to real-world deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to scalable systems and our SDK, helping customers integrate our technology into their apps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
